<item>
            <title>[LU-4372] Compatibility cache_register_net/cache_unregister_net for 2.6.36 kernels </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4372</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This problem is related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LU-4012&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;LU-4012&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
Kernel version 2.6.36 does not contain in net/sunrpc/cache.c the functions&lt;br/&gt;
cache_register_net/cache_unregister_net which are integrated in &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LU-4012&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;LU-4012&lt;/a&gt; for newer kernels (&amp;gt;= 3.4).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To provide compatibility for kernel versions 2.6.36 (used in 2.5 and 2.6) one needs&lt;br/&gt;
a compatibility macro.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will provide a patch to fix thos.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
